comments: Anunoby (TOR) and Paul (PHX) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players are in the lane.
Paul (PHX) places his arms against Barnes (TOR) with slight extension as he releases but the contact is marginal.
Paul (PHX) briefly grasps Barnes' (TOR) leg as he is coming off the pick.
Koloko (TOR) does not maintain verticality and initiates contact with Craig's (PHX) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) and Barnes (TOR) come together and mutually engage in marginal contact as Barnes is rolling toward the rim.
Bridges (PHX) briefly grasps Koloko's (TOR) arm as both players go for the loose ball.
Bridges (PHX) initiates contact with Koloko's (TOR) wrist and affects his shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Trent Jr. (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Trent Jr. is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs with Bridges (PHX) that affects his SQBR.
Ayton (PHX) extends both arms into Siakam (TOR) during his drive toward the rim. On contact, Siakam's SQBR is affected.
As Ayton (PHX) is moving to a vertical position, marginal arm contact occurs with Barnes (TOR) during his shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) and Siakam (TOR) mutually engage and disengage as both players are boxing out during the rebound attempt.
Wainright (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Barnes (TOR) during his drive toward the rim. Any ensuing contact is incidental.
Barnes (TOR) gets to ball height and maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Craig's (PHX) shot attempt.
Wainright (PHX) attempts to commit a take foul against Trent Jr. (TOR).
Wainright (PHX) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR).
Koloko (TOR) and Craig (PHX) come together during the rebound and marginal contact occurs as both players go for the loose ball.
